        "summary": "Get the current user's profile.",
        "description": "Returns the authenticated caller's identity and roles. In cookie mode the access token isn't readable by JS, so the SPA calls this on load to hydrate the session.\n\n**Errors:** 401 `common.unauthorized`, 429 `common.rate_limited`.",
        "operationId": "Me",
